{"tid":998104,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得自己試過點樣不顧一切去挽留一個人","createTime":"2019-01-27T16:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T10:34:59.000Z","uid":179084,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"270781ea9991142966c4ca78b8668faf92334ede","tid":998104,"uid":179084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"就算佢講野幾難聽都唔理 <br />\n仲傻傻地咁係佢屋企樓下等左幾個鐘<br />\n想同佢傾 求佢唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家想挽留既人 連見都無得見 <br />\n兩個係唔同地方 都唔敢去sd msg揾佢<br />\n驚只會令佢愈黎愈反感 朋友都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291dd58197780ef9f425761d75af0ce7161c4b90","tid":998104,"uid":78683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:52:44.000Z","msg":"你為咗佢連尊嚴都無埋 <br />\n但換嚟係一次又一次嘅傷心<br />\n何必"},{"pid":"9a5d619aee8c24d7e2975072b0840571a4c056f2","tid":998104,"uid":140130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"係佢面前喊"},{"pid":"c65d30882f1338476b44bea0048bdb8d1f0f5914","tid":998104,"uid":92042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"放低晒尊嚴佢挽留佢 求佢唔好走<br />\n最後都係走左 仲block埋我<br />\n而我 仲係好鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd10d6fd652961149de9f5dbfc8da87dc98bcdf","tid":998104,"uid":216030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"傷心換絕情"},{"pid":"27cfb2c3d281a6efab0bc94990a5acf58025a8f3","tid":998104,"uid":138040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"分手仲做乜朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係認真愛過就唔會"},{"pid":"d4d14ecbd69cdec150181dad75fb712557f65229","tid":998104,"uid":138040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd10d6fd652961149de9f5dbfc8da87dc98bcdf","tid":998104,"uid":216030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"傷心換絕情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:17:02.000Z","msg":"又見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28b72656440fc6b71c80efec57d130a00fe02d0","tid":998104,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"試過 對上發生<br />\n乜都無曬"},{"pid":"81b13cf3fa15883b38b8837108c1c4528d2cac7c","tid":998104,"uid":169266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:25:07.000Z","msg":"係佢屋企樓下由天光等到天黑 廁所都唔敢去<br />\n最後換黎嘅係咩都block哂 unfriend哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dc5467d09fe583a7bcc2be1c7839fd3790186c","tid":998104,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"好多年無呢d感覺"},{"pid":"1b24e5e971036ac9829702cd9407849f1fa9b78d","tid":998104,"uid":179084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:31:13.000Z","msg":"自己真係好蠢 又比人掉低係街 比佢打過 果時都可以唔識走 依然要同佢一齊。"},{"pid":"0cb996d5a95cb68778f4f0ea68f1e1772b24a81e","tid":998104,"uid":179084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27cfb2c3d281a6efab0bc94990a5acf58025a8f3","tid":998104,"uid":138040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"分手仲做乜朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係認真愛過就唔會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"何以見得"},{"pid":"d1846bd59fc4c56b4ac9d50b4b7a8867eacde359","tid":998104,"uid":138040,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0cb996d5a95cb68778f4f0ea68f1e1772b24a81e","tid":998104,"uid":179084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27cfb2c3d281a6efab0bc94990a5acf58025a8f3","tid":998104,"uid":138040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"分手仲做乜朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係認真愛過就唔會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"何以見得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:00:23.000Z","msg":"可能所經歷過嘅只有一兩段感情，入世未深咁<br />\n但我都有試過不顧一切地去挽留對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣變得冇哂尊嚴，係人生最唔開心嘅日子<br />\n當然，依段故事最後都要劃上句號<br />\n<br />\n好老實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔缺朋友<br />\n我唔想有一個冇可能起埋一齊嘅「朋友」<br />\n更加忍受唔到由愛侶關係要變返做朋友<br />\n係，分咗手仲企係對方角度諗、仲珍惜對方係好好<br />\n但問心嗰句....依種愛到底再係啲乜<br />\n再咁樣愛落去真係好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n我係好愛佢，但分咗手<br />\n我就要識得愛返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔再令自己痛心落去"},{"pid":"c240b40d92cbd674a6a8d479cd8ce00da844f100","tid":998104,"uid":138040,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"因為佢，每日任由酒精麻痹痛楚<br />\n因為佢，傷心到有過深度抑鬱<br />\n因為佢，差少少就放棄過生命<br />\n<br />\n望返以前自己傷心到變成咁<br />\n要身邊嘅朋友同屋企人擔心<br />\n又唔太覺係100%傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而更加清楚自己真係好愛佢<br />\n<br />\n愛得多就痛得多<br />\n唉，周不時仲會好掛住佢仲好愛佢<br />\n但咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情願連朋友都冇得做，自己一個FF好過"},{"pid":"20e8d7594005de6916a75b53c74e3967a167b135","tid":998104,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:14:09.000Z","msg":"喺佢樓下巴士站等佢佢嬲到告我性騷擾"},{"pid":"3161c91bb1ea4abe159e6c829b0d955c14ef4e46","tid":998104,"uid":201050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T20:59:01.000Z","msg":"曾經試過，仲要唔係求一次兩次，基本上持續左差唔多半年都挽留再一齊再挽留，當時同樓主一樣，而家發現自己真係好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  若果真係愛你珍惜你就唔需要你冇哂尊嚴咁去挽留佢，或者會因為你咁做而珍惜你，既然冇就唔需要為佢再折磨自己。 加油。<br />\n<br />\n利申:諗通之後放棄左好幾年，而家有個好愛我好珍惜我嘅人出現"},{"pid":"18726f66553f30413c2b7a85959a6af13a3a8bbc","tid":998104,"uid":49541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3161c91bb1ea4abe159e6c829b0d955c14ef4e46","tid":998104,"uid":201050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T20:59:01.000Z","msg":"曾經試過，仲要唔係求一次兩次，基本上持續左差唔多半年都挽留再一齊再挽留，當時同樓主一樣，而家發現自己真係好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/